'''Godfried Roemeratoe''' (born 19 August 1999) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] or [[Full back (association football)|right back]] for {{Dutch football updater|RKCWaalwi}} club [[RKC Waalwijk]].<ref name = "WF">{{Worldfootball.net|godfried-roemeratoe|new_id=pe425026}}</ref> Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].

==Club career==
Roemeratoe made his [[Eerste Divisie]] debut for [[FC Twente]] on 21 December 2018 in a game against [[N.E.C. (football club)|N.E.C.]] as a 90th-minute substitute for [[Matthew Smith (footballer, born 1999)|Matthew Smith]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2018/12/21/netherlands/eerste-divisie/stichting-fc-twente-65/nijmegen-eendracht-combinatie/2794558/|title=Game Report by Soccerway|date=21 December 2018}}</ref>

On 23 August 2021, he joined [[Willem II (football club)|Willem II]] on loan for the 2021–22 season.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Willem II (football club)|Willem II]]|url=https://www.willem-ii.nl/artikel/godfried-roemeratoe-naar-tilburg|title=Godfried Roemeratoe naar Tilburg|date=23 August 2021|accessdate=1 October 2021|language=nl}}</ref>

== International career ==
In March 2023, Roemeratoe received his first call-up to the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao senior national team]] for the [[2022–23 CONCACAF Nations League A|Nations League]] match against [[Canada men's national soccer team|Canada]] and the [[Exhibition game|friendly]] against [[Argentina national football team|Argentina]].<ref>{{cite web |date=14 March 2023 |title=PREPARASHONNAN TA KONTINUÁ PA NOS SELEKSHON NASHONAL ENFRENTÁ CANADA DJASABRA 25 MART PRÓKSIMO! NOS HUNGADÓNAN TA KONOSÍ! |url=https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=589715713200644 |access-date=17 March 2023 |website=facebook.com |publisher=[[Curaçao Football Federation]] |language=Papiamento}}</ref>

==Personal life==
Godfried is of Indonesian descent from his family name "Roemeratoe" which originates from [[Seram]] in the [[Maluku Islands]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Profil Godfried Roemeratoe, Pemain Keturunan Maluku yang Kini Bela Timnas Curacao|url=https://www.suara.com/bola/2023/03/07/215500/profil-godfried-roemeratoe-pemain-keturunan-maluku-yang-kini-bela-timnas-curacao|website=amp.suara.com|publisher=[[:id:Suara.com|Suara]]|access-date=2 May 2024|date=7 March 2023|first=Rully|last=Fauzi|language=id|trans-title=Profile of Godfried Roemeratoe, a player of Maluku descent who is now playing for the Curacao National Team}}</ref>

